'''Bananas''' were a [[Color/Legends|yellowish-green]] [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]] found in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. They sometimes had brown spots after growing too ripe. Bananas were typically the shape of a crescent.

